description: List the Sidewalk devices in an import task and their onboarding status.

parameters.name: Id
parameters.description: The identifier of the import task for which wireless devices are listed.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to get the next set of results, or null if there are no additional results.

nested_items.name: DestinationName
nested_items.description: The name of the Sidewalk destination that describes the IoT rule to route messages received from devices in an import task that are onboarded to AWS IoT Wireless.

nested_items.name: ImportedWirelessDeviceList
nested_items.description: List of wireless devices in an import task and their onboarding status.

nested_items.name: SidewalkManufacturingSn
nested_items.description: The Sidewalk manufacturing serial number (SMSN) of the Sidewalk device.

nested_items.name: OnboardingStatus
nested_items.description: The onboarding status of the Sidewalk device in the import task.

nested_items.name: OnboardingStatusReason
nested_items.description: The reason for the onboarding status information for the Sidewalk device.

nested_items.name: LastUpdateTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the status information was last updated.
